Bayer to Spend $22.3 Billion on R&D, Capital Projects by 2013

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-04-29T08:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-29/bayer-to-spend-22-3-billion-on-r-d-capital-projects-by-2013.html
Bayer AG (BAYN)  plans to invest 15 billion
euros ($22.3 billion) in research and development and  capital
spending  through 2013, Chief Executive Officer Marijn Dekkers
said.  About two thirds of the money will go to research, with one
third for capital projects, Dekkers said in remarks prepared for
